OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1775661069
OL,3,CMasked thieves steal up to #25k of
OL,4,CPokemon cards in gaming shop
OL,6,FA Gloucester gaming shop owner says he
OL,7,Fhas been left in 'shock' after Pokemon
OL,8,Ftrading cards worth around #25,000
OL,9,Fwere stolen by masked thieves in a
OL,10,Fburglary.
OL,12,FThe break-in happened at Full Fire TCG
OL,13,FGloucester during the night on
OL,14,FFebruary 21.
OL,16,FCCTV footage captured three suspects,
OL,17,Fone armed with a crowbar, spending
OL,18,Fapproximately 30 minutes inside the
OL,19,Fstore.
OL,26,@lD@DrroD@crr
