OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1775661069
OL,3,CMasked thieves steal up to #25k of
OL,4,CPokemon cards in gaming shop
OL,6,FBen Powell, a passionate card game
OL,7,Fenthusiast who opened the shop just 15
OL,8,Fmonths ago, described his reaction
OL,9,Fafter seeing the CCTV.
OL,11,F"I woke up in a panic," he said.
OL,13,F"It's remarkable, but Pokemon cards
OL,14,Fhave become a genuine investment item.
OL,16,F"While the individual cards in the
OL,17,Fcabinets were valued at between #5 and
OL,18,F#50 each, when you consider that
OL,19,Faround 600 were taken, the cumulative
OL,20,Floss is a significant sum."
OL,26,@lD@DrruD@Zrr
