OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1775661069
OL,3,CMasked thieves steal up to #25k of
OL,4,CPokemon cards in gaming shop
OL,6,FWhat are Pokemon cards?
OL,8,FPokemon Trading Card Game is a
OL,9,Fcollectible card game based on the
OL,10,FPokemon franchise, where players build
OL,11,Fdecks and battle each other using
OL,12,Fcards representing Pokemon creatures,
OL,13,Ftrainer items, and energy resources.
OL,15,FThe cards became a global phenomenon.
OL,16,FToday they are collected both for
OL,17,Fgameplay and as valuable collectibles
OL,18,Fwith rare and vintage cards can sell
OL,19,Ffor tens of thousands of pounds.
OL,26,@lD@DrrnD@MrrpD@DrrrD@DrrtD@Wrr
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
