FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1775661069
OL,3,CMasked thieves steal up to #25k of
OL,4,CPokemon cards in gaming shop
OL,6,FTo prevent future incidents, Ben says
OL,7,Fhe has taken precautionary measures
OL,8,Fincluding the installation of window
OL,9,Fbars and relocating his most valuable
OL,10,Fcards to a secure location.
OL,12,FBen continues to appeal for anyone
OL,13,Fwith information to come forward.
OL,15,FGloucestershire Police have confirmed
OL,16,Fthat officers attended the scene and
OL,17,Fremain in contact with Ben as the
OL,18,Finvestigation progresses.
OL,26,@lD@Drr
